com.amazonaws.greengrass.javasdk

Class IotDataClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.greengrass.javasdk.IotDataClient

  • public class IotDataClient
extends Object
    Iot Data client interacts with IPC. It implements a broker for applications and things to publish messages over HTTP (Publish) and retrieve, update, and delete thing shadows.
